# Post-install scripts directory
# 
# Scripts in this directory can be executed during the build process
# by setting the POST_INSTALL_SCRIPT build arg to the script name.
#
# Scripts have access to:
# - TARGETARCH: Target architecture (amd64, arm64, etc.)
# - UBUNTU_RELEASE: Ubuntu version being used
# - STAGING_ROOT: Path to the staging rootfs (default: /staging-rootfs)
# - Any other build args passed via docker-bake.hcl
#
# Example scripts:
# - install-bun.sh: Installs Bun runtime
# - install-uv.sh: Could install Python uv package manager
# - install-deno.sh: Could install Deno runtime
